            </member>
        </simplelist>
    </refsection>
    <refsection>
        <title>Used Functions</title>
        <para>
            The <literal>range</literal> function is based on the <link linkend="rowcomp">rowcomp</link> function
            which uses the <link linkend="svd">svd</link> decomposition.
        </para>
    </refsection>
</refentry>
